dataLineage.statement:
Admin 1 layer was downloaded from the OCHA COD Registry. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Attribution errors were corrected and the geometry was updated by dissolving an admin 2 layer that had its attributes and topology cleaned. The layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS:
1. Created and populated admin 0 name and pcode fields. 2. Created and populated a reference name field. 3. Admin 1 name field changed to proper case from ALL CAPS. 4. Pcodes were fully constructed by adding admin 0 portion ("CO"). 5. Fixed gap and overlap errors in geometry.
